{"tid":1351872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班友咪撚on9喇 人地出黑社會就驚 點撚樣抗爭啊","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:49:22.000Z","uid":18648,"like":103,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"479f068ea06864d9ea5b92e98d83ab506492c338","tid":1351872,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講無預過警黑合作<br />\n如果班狗次次都出黑社會<br />\n咁係咪我地次撚次都唔洗出？<br />\n<br />\n革命就係要用血用汗<br />\n就係要勇往直前 <span style=\"color: red;\">排除萬難</span><br />\n不進則退啊 明唔撚明啊<br />\n<br />\n今次我地比人踩到上心口<br />\n咁都唔還拖<br />\n對唔對得住坐緊嘅義士同烈士啊<br />\n<br />\n爭取民主<br />\n就咩都唔可以怕<br />\n無論對手幾強大<br />\n點都唔可以退縮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗嘅手足<br />\n你地嘅責任唔係叫人唔好光復<br />\n而係應該做地圖撚<br />\n建議人點進點退<br />\n咁先係真正救到香港同班兄弟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n乜都驚<br />\n又驚危險又驚比人圍<br />\n香港點會有出路啊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有危先有機</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXARtfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXARtfJ.png&h=bf330fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位真義士真香港人<br />\n星期六 廿七號見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c945d0c47a794bc6cce33626d370a892900edfc0","tid":1351872,"uid":66390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"27/7 為香港版國定殺戮日 （元朗區） 全城開火！文宣組 行動組 物資組 全面進場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350317</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警開槍都未驚呀 點解要驚元朗黑社會呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351170\" data-auto-link target=